          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_213_sideB_3.mp3"
        }
      ],
      "note": "**[misc:11]**"
    },
    {
      "cardId": "dummy_214",
      "cardType": "flippable",
      "sideA": "Sobre la marcha iré documentando lo realizado.",
      "sideB": [
        {
          "text": "I will document what's been done on the fly.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_214_sideB_0.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "I'll document what is done as we go.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_214_sideB_1.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "I'll document my progress as I go.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_214_sideB_2.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "On the fly, I will document what's been done.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_214_sideB_3.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "As I go, I'll document my progress.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_214_sideB_4.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "On the fly, I will document what is done.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_214_sideB_5.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "I will document what is done on the fly.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_214_sideB_6.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "On the spot, I will document what is done.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_214_sideB_7.mp3"
        }
      ],
      "note": "**[misc:11]**\n\n~On the fly, I will document what it's done~ is incorrect because [what it is done] or [what it has done] does not fit the passive meaning needed here. You should use [what's been done] or [what is done] without the pronoun [it]."
    },
    {
      "cardId": "dummy_215",
      "cardType": "flippable",
      "sideA": "No ha sido implementado aun esa funcion.",
      "sideB": [
        {
          "text": "That feature hasn't been implemented yet.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_215_sideB_0.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "That function has not been implemented yet.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_215_sideB_1.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "That feature is not implemented yet.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_215_sideB_2.mp3"
        }
      ],
      "note": "~It hasn't been implemented that feature yet~ has an unnatural word order. The subject [that feature] should come before the passive verb [hasn't been implemented].\n\n~That feature doesn't implement yet~ uses the active voice incorrectly. Since a feature cannot implement itself, you must use the passive voice [isn't implemented] or [hasn't been implemented]."
    },
