      "note": "~I don't have the meeting's invitation~ sounds slightly unnatural. For events, it is better to use a compound noun like [the meeting invitation] or use the preposition [to] as in [the invitation to the meeting]."
    },
    {
      "cardId": "dummy_223",
      "cardType": "flippable",
      "sideA": "Que hay acerca de la reunión de hoy.",
      "sideB": [
        {
          "text": "What about today's meeting?",
