      "note": "**[pv:59]**\n\n**[er:103]**\n\n~I found out that this morning.~ is not valid because 'find out' requires 'about' when followed by a noun or pronoun object. Use [found out about].\n\n~I knew that this morning~ is incorrect for expressing discovery. The verb [know] describes the continuous state of having information, not the moment you acquire it. To express 'enterarse', you must use an action verb like [found out] or [heard]."
